The people at Som Livre in Brasil have sponsored and recorded a wonderful homage concert tribute to Tom Jobim [Antonio Carlos Jobim if you will!].
 But, the music! It is grand and each of the current Brasilian talents perform with marvelous talent. And the quality of the sound is sensational too. Like Bacharach here in North America, Jobim in South America wrote such grand material that it sounds great whether sung Bossa Nova style or Caberate or Rap!
